9
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:32,670
Let's go!

10
00:00:32,790 --> 00:00:34,790
Why are you taking the kids with you?

11
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,640
I didn't scold or beat them.

12
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:39,110
Zhang Fengxia, tell him

13
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:40,350
to go home with me.

14
00:00:40,350 --> 00:00:42,280
Your eggs. I don't want your money.

15
