19
00:00:48,190 --> 00:00:49,790
Give me another crate of wine.

20
00:00:49,790 --> 00:00:51,420
You have too many unpaid tabs. I can't accept any more.

21
00:00:51,420 --> 00:00:52,230
I'm going to bed.

22
00:00:52,230 --> 00:00:53,630
Let's go.

23
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:55,950
Go.

24
00:00:56,150 --> 00:00:58,610
Murat, stop drinking. I'm closing the door.

25
00:00:58,980 --> 00:00:59,580
Zhang Fengxia.

26
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,620
You might not be able to come back later.
There's a snowstorm today.

27
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:02,940
When I come back,

28
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:06,070
I might drive my

29
