You'd better ride a horse.

31
00:01:10,030 --> 00:01:11,110
If you drive now, it'd be considered drunk driving.

32
00:01:11,110 --> 00:01:12,240
They'll arrest you.

33
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:18,340
I'm the king of the snowfield. I'm not afraid.

34
00:01:19,510 --> 00:01:21,840
You might as well freeze to death outside.

35
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:24,220
